ZH: 生态环境对我们的生活非常重要。
EN: The ecological environment is very important to our lives.

ZH: 我们应该保护好生态，共同建设美丽家园。
EN: We should protect the ecology and build a beautiful home together.

ZH: 这个国家对生态建设投入了大量的资金。
EN: This country has invested a lot of funds in ecological construction.

ZH: 生态保护需要全社会的共同努力。
EN: Ecological protection requires the joint efforts of the whole society.

ZH: 生态破坏会导致很多灾难性的后果。
EN: Ecological destruction can lead to many disastrous consequences.

ZH: 污染对生态平衡有着严重的影响。
EN: Pollution has a serious impact on ecological balance.

ZH: 生态学研究了生物与环境的相互关系。
EN: Ecology studies the relationship between organisms and the environment.

ZH: 这片地区的生态系统已经遭受了很大的破坏。
EN: The ecosystem in this area has suffered significant damage.

ZH: 改善生态环境是一项长期而艰巨的任务。
EN: Improving the ecological environment is a long-term and arduous task.

ZH: 生态旅游可以促进当地经济的发展。
EN: Ecotourism can promote the development of the local economy.

ZH: 这个城市注重生态建设，环境非常优美。
EN: This city pays attention to ecological construction and has a beautiful environment.

ZH: 科技的发展也给生态系统带来了好处。
EN: Technological development has also brought benefits to the ecosystem.

ZH: 保护野生动物是保护生态的重要一环。
EN: Protecting wildlife is an important part of ecological conservation.

ZH: 生态农业可提供健康的食品和保护土地资源。
EN: Ecological agriculture can provide healthy food and protect land resources.

ZH: 这个国家的政府制定了严格的生态法规。
EN: The government of this country has enacted strict ecological regulations.

ZH: 生态环境的改善对人们的身心健康有着积极的影响。
EN: The improvement of the ecological environment has a positive impact on people's physical and mental health.

ZH: 生态恢复需要人们的共同努力和智慧。
EN: Ecological restoration requires the joint efforts and wisdom of people.

ZH: 森林是地球上最重要的生态资源之一。
EN: Forests are one of the most important ecological resources on Earth.

